name: Calamari Bathe & Binge

reviews.review_text:
Located in front of Santana Beach Resort in Candolim, Calamari offers a prime beachfront dining experience. The restaurant's convenient location makes it easily accessible for both locals and tourists staying in the area.

Calamari in Goa is a fantastic place to enjoy a meal right by the beach. It's conveniently located with plenty of parking, and the restaurant itself is large and spacious, providing ample room for a comfortable dining experience. While there are a few shacks available, they tend to fill up quickly around sunset, so it's wise to arrive early if you want a prime spot.

We tried the Fish and Chips, and it was excellent. The fish was fresh, and the chips had the perfect amount of crispiness. The service was commendable, with friendly and attentive staff. However, the prices are a bit higher than what you might typically find in Goa these days, but the quality of the food and the overall experience make it worthwhile. In summary, Calamari is a great option for dining in Goa, especially if you're seeking a spacious and well-situated restaurant with delicious food.

It's lovely, they have a candle light set up with live music,a white set up, with big pedestal  fan installed, and small ceiling fan at each set up.  The area is wide enough to accommodate 100 people in one go.
People can enter right from the candolim beach itself, it has a beach entrance,
Taste is super delicious, but vegetarian dishes are limited.

Great view, very convenient location in candolim. I would suggest to reserve a table before going if you want to sit near the beach. The food is always a hit here and then portions are good too. Service was fast and professional. It's a very beautiful shack that's very well managed.

description:
### Calamari Bathe & Binge: A Beachfront Culinary Gem in Goa

Rated a commendable **4.4** based on nearly **8,966 reviews**, Calamari Bathe & Binge offers a vibrant and captivating dining experience that beautifully marries the charm of Goan cuisine with the allure of beachside luxury. Nestled conveniently in front of the Santana Beach Resort in Candolim, this restaurant has garnered a loyal clientele with its popular tags, including "shack" (229 mentions), "band" (113 mentions), "sunset" (103 mentions), and "goan" (62 mentions), highlighting its essence as a local hotspot for both tourists and residents alike.

### Ambiance & Design

As one approaches Calamari, the inviting atmosphere beckons you with an elegant white setup adorned with candles and the gentle strumming of live music. Optimally designed to accommodate **up to 100 guests**, the spacious layout features comfortable seating arrangements with both large pedestal fans and smaller ceiling fans ensuring a breezy ambiance. The restaurant’s layout cleverly utilizes its beachfront location, allowing diners direct access to the sandy shores, with a picturesque view that becomes even more stunning as the sun dips below the horizon, creating a sought-after sunset experience.

![Calamari Bathe & Binge](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdn3d0R_jj5NfSroZ34PVqGu_zbq0Lwpikouxz4mQia6D6P-98Sw0di02-JAD8VN1byaEuRccF4q6QqhHKgw9-Ub1IgMh5p5b3FK8r_ILPKqGLdmXdKOAg-4uH8TgGfpDzxDM3EkRQ=w375-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Calamari is celebrated for its delectable offerings, with standout dishes like the **Fish and Chips** receiving rave reviews for its fresh catch and perfectly crispy fries. Guests highlight that while the seafood is abundant and flavorsome, vegetarian options may feel limited. The presentation of the dishes reflects a thoughtful touch, with vibrant colors and appealing arrangements that elevate the dining experience. Diners often express their satisfaction with generous portion sizes that ensure no one leaves hungry.

![Fish and Chips](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm6tcJH43MDpehOqMZkXSCnyigka6AIL_wXSA-JSkc3ewMNntRfokUm2TbR8Bee3v6WTCDedJhNix8hhuNwGsm-Mg5Y7EwYrq9Yo25AW58ZPV5wLpdhLZ_mG6vp5VH_TvefCy6F=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

At Calamari, the customer experience is enriched by the friendly demeanor of the staff, noted for their attentiveness and professional service. Many patrons recommend reserving a table, particularly those preferring an ocean-view sunset dining. While some guests mention that prices are on the higher side compared to local shacks, they agree that the quality of food and the overall ambiance justify the expense.

![Dining Setup](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmSR030jHCA6vNPUJTXSIcFYeabFecVv1XRILvE-7sMwDPqsVBaYBBRcKRPY_X8rCYlJ7zBJZdZOimkLnW0gpR47Hm5YB5UcDq9sNLe8Uwy89uNOMJ8A96VPPNQFuz6K9gyKMWJ=w375-h281-p)

### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz around Calamari is palpable, as evidenced by the substantial number of reviews on various platforms that consistently affirm its reputation for quality. Diners rave about the seamless combination of delightful food, beautiful views, and the lively atmosphere created by the live bands that perform, enhancing the experience, especially during twilight hours. This energetic vibe, coupled with its strategic beachfront location, makes Calamari Bathe & Binge a must-visit when in Goa.

### Conclusion

In summary, Calamari Bathe & Binge stands tall as an ideal dining destination for those craving a blend of exquisite Goan cuisine, beautiful decor, and breathtaking views. The restaurant not only promises memorable meals against the backdrop of serene sunsets but also delights guests with its warm service and vibrant atmosphere, cementing its status as a cherished spot in Goa’s culinary landscape. Whether you're a local or a traveler, Calamari invites you to kick back, sip on a drink, and indulge in the flavors of the coast.
